items.title: Morazha Co-operative Arts and Science College popu...
items.content:
Morazha Co-operative Arts and Science College popularly known as STEMS College Morazha is a Higher Educational Institution that is being managed and operated under Morazha Educational Co-operative Society Ltd. No. C 1742. The founding vision of the society is to offer quality education at an affordable cost under a cooperative framework
We are committed to promoting social justice and ensuring accessibility to higher education to the underprivileged. Most of the beneficiaries of this college are economically and socially backward classes. The institution is committed to fostering an educational environment that is both engaging and inclusive, one that supports the dreams, talents, and aspirations of every student.
